    {
      "id": "PopularPost134601",
      "post_content": "I found many aspects of the Kamigawa block to be very \"meh\", but I've got to say - they had a few instances of outstanding flavour text ([Wandering Ones](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Wandering Ones)). I really like this little excerpt of a letter from [Hisoka, Minamo Sensei](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Hisoka, Minamo Sensei) to [Konda, Lord of Eiganjo](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Konda, Lord of Eiganjo); it does a good job conveying how the greed of Konda was condemning **every mortal creature** on Kamigawa to a brutal war.   \n  \nIn fact, Hisoka is repeating himself here! Check out the flavour text for [Night of Souls' Betrayal](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Night of Souls' Betrayal), and the text on [Hero's Demise](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Hero's Demise). ",
      "posted_by": "Leshrac_Nightwalker",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost134601\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_post\">I found many aspects of the Kamigawa block to be very \"meh\", but I've got to say - they had a few instances of outstanding flavour text (<a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Wandering Ones\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Wandering Ones\">Wandering Ones</a>).  I really like this little excerpt of a letter from <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Hisoka, Minamo Sensei\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Hisoka, Minamo Sensei\">Hisoka, Minamo Sensei</a> to <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Konda, Lord of Eiganjo\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Konda, Lord of Eiganjo\">Konda, Lord of Eiganjo</a>; it does a good job conveying how the greed of Konda was condemning <b>every mortal creature</b> on Kamigawa to a brutal war.  <br/><br/>In fact, Hisoka is repeating himself here!  Check out the flavour text for <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Night of Souls' Betrayal\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Night of Souls' Betrayal\">Night of Souls' Betrayal</a>, and the text on <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Hero's Demise\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Hero's Demise\">Hero's Demise</a>.  </span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '134601'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n               