    {
      "id": "PopularPost281380",
      "post_content": "I think Splice would've made this playable. Being able to convert your cheap burn spells into acceleration to a creature you top-deck might be handy.  \n  \n@AXER: There are no sorceries with Splice because then they could be \"cast\" while normal sorceries couldn't. Costs are balanced around a card's casting speed, and as silly as it may sound, there are uses for haste at instant speed. Someone uses something that enables you to drop a [Prodigal Pyromancer](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Prodigal Pyromancer) during your turn (I don't know, maybe they're using a [Hunted Wumpus](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Hunted Wumpus)?) and you need to tap for that one damage? Instant speed haste has your back.",
      "posted_by": "DoragonShinzui",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost281380\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_post\">I think Splice would've made this playable. Being able to convert your cheap burn spells into acceleration to a creature you top-deck might be handy.<br/><br/>@AXER: There are no sorceries with Splice because then they could be \"cast\" while normal sorceries couldn't. Costs are balanced around a card's casting speed, and as silly as it may sound, there are uses for haste at instant speed. Someone uses something that enables you to drop a <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Prodigal Pyromancer\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Prodigal Pyromancer\">Prodigal Pyromancer</a> during your turn (I don't know, maybe they're using a <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Hunted Wumpus\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Hunted Wumpus\">Hunted Wumpus</a>?) and you need to tap for that one damage? Instant speed haste has your back.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '281380'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy79844\">DoragonShinzui</span>\r\n                                (11/13/2012 7:03:28 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                       